The paper deals with scene text detection using deep learning methods, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves combining ideas from two existing methods, which requires a certain level of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) expertise. The paper also involves segmentation of text regions, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
